summary:
K ENB, Real Vision ENB, Project ENB, E ENB, Skylight ENB, Sharpshooters ENB...
Great Names Great Presets, but none of them FULLY fits my taste so I started mixing and tweaking...
Now I'm in A state where i think i can Upload this ENB for you to test what you think.
descriptionHtml:
I like natural, realistic enviroments, and this is what this ENB should achieve, Im not e good coder nor a Screenarcher (you will see in the screenshots).

But this is just an ENB setting for those who don't want to stick to one of the "AAA" ENB's mentioned in the small description.

Also this is meant to be played, not just to go screenarchering. Have fun and thank you.

I will edit the description another time, just the most necessary details:

Turn the ingame brightness down!

Natural enviroment:

Dark nights (DARK)
TOD(sunsets,sunrise usw. gives a good mood)
Saturated(not oversaturated)
All effects of ENB used.
Merged sweetfx suite (between realvision ultra+i can't believe it's not a ENB)

Will work on this ENB as much as i can, requests are welcome :)

A Extreme Version (Most effect on -1) and a not so Extreme Version 1 and 0 of the effects) is provided.




For the actual ENB ( 244)

Download here:

http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.html

Visual Mods I use (Lighting):

Climates of Tamriel:

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17802//?

(no interior, night or dungeon setting)

In conjunction with realistic nights:

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49472/?

Also use ELE and his instructions:

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27022/?

ELFX (careful with ELE)

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27043/?

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/32064//?

I use Realistic water two and watercolormod for it:

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41076/?

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/48938/?tab=1&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D48938%26preview%3D&pUp=1
